<text>James or Jim Craig may refer to:
==Entertainment==
* James Humbert Craig (1877–1944), Irish painter
* James Craig (actor) (1912–1985), American actor
* James Craig (&quot;General Hospital&quot;), fictional character on television, a.k.a. Jerry Jacks
